genresAdvancedInfo.name: terrorcore
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Terrorcore is a subgenre of hardcore techno and gabber that emerged in the late 1990s. It is characterized by its extremely fast and aggressive beats, dark and often violent themes, and use of horror movie samples and sound effects.
